sql_query:
SELECT 
    ad.id, 
    ad.appointment_date, 
    cm.city_name, 
    ad.scan_name, 
    ad.test_name, 
    spcd.center_name, 
    ad.amount, 
    ad.appointment_status,
    ad."createdAt",
    ad."updatedAt"
FROM 
    public.appointment_details ad
JOIN 
    public.city_masters cm ON ad.city_id = cm.id AND cm.is_deleted = false
JOIN 
    public.service_provider_center_details spcd ON ad.center_id = spcd.id AND spcd.is_deleted = false
WHERE 
    ad.is_deleted = false
ORDER BY 
    ad.appointment_date  DESC;
